  1â†’# Room Display Features Guide
  2â†’
  3â†’## QR Code - Quick Book
  4â†’
  5â†’### What It Does
  6â†’Displays a scannable QR code on the room display that allows employees to quickly book the meeting room using their mobile device.
  7â†’
  8â†’### How It Works
  9â†’
 10â†’1. **QR Code Generation**
 11â†’   - Uses free API: `https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/`
 12â†’   - Generates a 200x200px QR code
 13â†’   - Points to: `{origin}/modules/meetings/new?roomId={roomId}`
 14â†’
 15â†’2. **User Flow**
 16â†’   ```
 17â†’   Employee â†’ Scans QR code on room display
 18â†’           â†’ Opens booking page on phone
 19â†’           â†’ Pre-filled with room ID
 20â†’           â†’ Fills in meeting details
 21â†’           â†’ Submits booking
 22â†’   ```
 23â†’
 24â†’3. **Location**
 25â†’   - Right sidebar of room display
 26â†’   - Above "Next Meeting" widget
 27â†’   - Always visible
 28â†’
 29â†’### Implementation
 30â†’
 31â†’**Code Location:** `src/routes/(fullscreen)/display/room/[roomId]/+page.svelte`
 32â†’
 33â†’**QR Code URL Function:**
 34â†’```typescript
 35â†’function getQRCodeUrl(url: string) {
 36â†’  return `https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=200x200&data=${encodeURIComponent(url)}`;
 37â†’}
 38â†’```
 39â†’
 40â†’**Booking URL:**
 41â†’```typescript
 42â†’bookingUrl = `${window.location.origin}/modules/meetings/new?roomId=${roomId}`;
 43â†’```
 44â†’
 45â†’**Render:**
 46â†’```svelte
 47â†’<div class="qr-section">
 48â†’  <div class="qr-label">QUICK BOOK</div>
 49â†’  <div class="qr-code">
 50â†’    {#if bookingUrl}
 51â†’      <img src={getQRCodeUrl(bookingUrl)} alt="Scan to book this room" class="qr-image" />
 52â†’    {:else}
 53â†’      <div class="qr-placeholder">Loading...</div>
 54â†’    {/if}
 55â†’  </div>
 56â†’</div>
 57â†’```
 58â†’
