 61â†’## Check-In Feature
 62â†’
 63â†’### What It Does
 64â†’Allows meeting participants to check in to the current meeting using:
 65â†’1. **Employee ID** (manual entry)
 66â†’2. **QR Code scan** (coming soon)
 67â†’
 68â†’### How It Works
 69â†’
 70â†’1. **Trigger Check-In**
 71â†’   - Click "CHECK IN" button (appears when meeting is active)
 72â†’   - Button location: Right sidebar, when `roomData.currentMeeting` exists
 73â†’
 74â†’2. **Check-In Modal**
 75â†’   ```
 76â†’   User clicks "CHECK IN"
 77â†’   â†’ Modal appears with:
 78â†’      - Meeting title
 79â†’      - Employee ID input field
 80â†’      - QR scanner placeholder
 81â†’      - Submit/Cancel buttons
 82â†’   ```
 83â†’
 84â†’3. **Manual Check-In Flow**
 85â†’   ```
 86â†’   User enters Employee ID (e.g., E12345)
 87â†’   â†’ Clicks "Check In" button
 88â†’   â†’ POST /api/v1/meetings/{meetingId}/checkin
 89â†’   â†’ Server validates employee
 90â†’   â†’ Success: Shows confirmation
 91â†’   â†’ Failure: Shows error message
 92â†’   ```
 93â†’
 94â†’### Implementation
 95â†’
 96â†’**Check-In Button:**
 97â†’```svelte
 98â†’{#if roomData.currentMeeting}
 99â†’  <div class="current-meeting-widget">
100â†’    <div class="widget-label">ENDS</div>
101â†’    <div class="end-time">{formatTime(roomData.currentMeeting.endTime)}</div>
102â†’    <button class="checkin-btn-small" onclick={handleCheckin}>
103â†’      CHECK IN
104â†’    </button>
105â†’  </div>
106â†’{/if}
107â†’```
108â†’
109â†’**Handle Check-In:**
110â†’```typescript
111â†’function handleCheckin() {
112â†’  isCheckinMode = true;         // Open modal
113â†’  employeeIdInput = '';         // Clear input
114â†’  checkinError = '';            // Clear errors
115â†’}
116â†’```
117â†’
118â†’**Submit Check-In:**
119â†’```typescript
120â†’async function handleCheckinSubmit() {
121â†’  if (!employeeIdInput.trim()) {
122â†’    checkinError = 'Please enter your Employee ID';
123â†’    return;
124â†’  }
125â†’
126â†’  if (!roomData.currentMeeting) {
127â†’    checkinError = 'No active meeting to check in to';
128â†’    return;
129â†’  }
130â†’
131â†’  checkingIn = true;
132â†’  checkinError = '';
133â†’
134â†’  try {
135â†’    const response = await fetch(`/api/v1/meetings/${roomData.currentMeeting.id}/checkin`, {
136â†’      method: 'POST',
137â†’      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
138â†’      body: JSON.stringify({
139â†’        employeeId: employeeIdInput.trim(),
140â†’        method: 'manual'
141â†’      })
142â†’    });
143â†’
144â†’    const result = await response.json();
145â†’
146â†’    if (result.success) {
147â†’      alert(`Check-in successful!\nMeeting: ${result.data.meetingTitle}`);
148â†’      isCheckinMode = false;
149â†’      loadSchedule(); // Refresh to update status
150â†’    } else {
151â†’      checkinError = result.error || 'Check-in failed';
152â†’    }
153â†’  } catch (error) {
154â†’    console.error('Check-in error:', error);
155â†’    checkinError = 'Failed to connect to server';
156â†’  } finally {
157â†’    checkingIn = false;
158â†’  }
159â†’}
160â†’```
161â†’
162â†’**Modal UI:**
163â†’```svelte
164â†’{#if isCheckinMode}
165â†’  <div class="modal">
166â†’    <div class="modal-content">
167â†’      <h2>Check In</h2>
168â†’      {#if roomData.currentMeeting}
169â†’        <p class="meeting-info">Meeting: <strong>{roomData.currentMeeting.title}</strong></p>
170â†’      {/if}
171â†’      <p>Scan your QR code or enter your employee ID</p>
172â†’
173â†’      <div class="qr-scanner">
174â†’        <div class="scanner-frame">
175â†’          ğŸ“· QR Scanner (Coming Soon)
176â†’        </div>
177â†’      </div>
178â†’
179â†’      <input
180â†’        type="text"
181â†’        placeholder="Enter Employee ID (e.g., E12345)"
182â†’        class="employee-id-input"
183â†’        bind:value={employeeIdInput}
184â†’        disabled={checkingIn}
185â†’        onkeydown={(e) => e.key === 'Enter' && handleCheckinSubmit()}
186â†’      />
187â†’
188â†’      {#if checkinError}
189â†’        <div class="checkin-error">
190â†’          âš ï¸ {checkinError}
191â†’        </div>
192â†’      {/if}
193â†’
194â†’      <div class="modal-actions">
195â†’        <button class="btn-cancel" onclick={() => isCheckinMode = false} disabled={checkingIn}>
196â†’          Cancel
197â†’        </button>
198â†’        <button class="btn-submit" onclick={handleCheckinSubmit}
199â†’                disabled={checkingIn || !employeeIdInput.trim()}>
200â†’          {checkingIn ? 'Checking in...' : 'Check In'}
201â†’        </button>
202â†’      </div>
203â†’    </div>
204â†’  </div>
205â†’{/if}
206â†’```
207â†’
208â†’### API Endpoint
209â†’
210â†’**POST** `/api/v1/meetings/{id}/checkin`
211â†’
212â†’**Request Body:**
213â†’```json
214â†’{
215â†’  "userId": "123456",  // NIK (Nomor Induk Karyawan)
216â†’  "method": "manual",
217â†’  "isExternal": false
218â†’}
219â†’```
220â†’
221â†’**Success Response:**
222â†’```json
223â†’{
224â†’  "success": true,
225â†’  "message": "Check-in successful",
226â†’  "data": {
227â†’    "meetingId": "meeting123",
228â†’    "meetingTitle": "Project Planning",
229â†’    "type": "internal",
230â†’    "userId": "123456",
231â†’    "name": "Employee Name",
232â†’    "email": "employee@company.com",
233â†’    "checkinTime": "2025-01-12T10:30:00Z",
234â†’    "method": "manual"
235â†’  }
236â†’}
237â†’```
238â†’
239â†’**Error Response:**
240â†’```json
241â†’{
242â†’  "success": false,
243â†’  "error": "Employee not found" // No invitation required - anyone can check in
244â†’}
245â†’```
