333â†’## Troubleshooting
334â†’
335â†’### QR Code Not Showing
336â†’
337â†’**Check:**
338â†’1. Is `bookingUrl` set? (Check browser console)
339â†’2. Is the API accessible? (Check network tab)
340â†’3. Image blocked by firewall/CSP?
341â†’
342â†’**Debug:**
343â†’```typescript
344â†’console.log('Booking URL:', bookingUrl);
345â†’console.log('QR Code URL:', getQRCodeUrl(bookingUrl));
346â†’```
347â†’
348â†’**Fix:**
349â†’- Ensure `onMount` runs and sets `bookingUrl`
350â†’- Check Content Security Policy allows external images
351â†’- Verify API is accessible: `https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/`
352â†’
353â†’### Check-In Button Not Working
354â†’
355â†’**Check:**
356â†’1. Is there an active meeting? (`roomData.currentMeeting`)
357â†’2. Is modal appearing? (z-index issue?)
358â†’3. Any JavaScript errors in console?
359â†’
360â†’**Debug:**
361â†’```typescript
362â†’function handleCheckin() {
363â†’  console.log('Check-in clicked!');
364â†’  console.log('Current meeting:', roomData.currentMeeting);
365â†’  isCheckinMode = true;
366â†’}
367â†’```
368â†’
369â†’**Fix:**
370â†’- Modal has `z-index: 2000` (should be visible above all)
371â†’- Button only shows when `roomData.currentMeeting` exists
372â†’- Check browser console for errors
373â†’
374â†’### Check-In Submission Fails
375â†’
376â†’**Check:**
377â†’1. Is API endpoint implemented? (`/api/v1/meetings/{id}/checkin`)
378â†’2. Employee ID valid?
379â†’3. Network errors?
380â†’
381â†’**Debug:**
382â†’```typescript
383â†’console.log('Submitting check-in for:', employeeIdInput);
384â†’console.log('Meeting ID:', roomData.currentMeeting.id);
385â†’```
386â†’
387â†’**Common Errors:**
388â†’- `"Employee not found"` - Invalid employee ID
389â†’- `"Employee not invited"` - Employee not in participant list
390â†’- `"No active meeting"` - Meeting already ended
391â†’- `"Failed to connect"` - API endpoint not implemented
